      <title>网络攻击者从澳大利亚养老基金中窃取了数千人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/australian-pensions-suffer-cyber-attack-on-thousands-of-accounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该国顶级养老基金Australiansuper的一些成员在整个行业的网络攻击中损失了大量退休储蓄，这可能损害了数千人的个人数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/australian-pensions-suffer-cyber-attack-on-thousands-of-accounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 01:19:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
